{"tid":729833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：壞事做多，不問蒼生問鬼神","createTime":"2018-07-05T01:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:58:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"36682d9649a4c1920c5e1d073426933aea9e7cad","tid":729833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"台灣總統蔡英文日前在台中市長林佳龍的陪同下，到東區信義街的福德祠參訪；林佳龍透露，總統此行有還願的成份。對此，人民日報海外網3日刊文指出，蔡英文的行為是「不問蒼師問鬼神」，2年多大戲不斷上演。<br />\n<br />\n文章引用《ETtoday新聞雲》的報導指出，蔡英文2012年曾具名贈匾給福德祠，未料當年蔡英文未當選總統，有人建議拿下匾額，換另一個人的匾額（指前總統馬英九），但福德祠堅持「她一定會當選總統」，後來蔡英文果真在2016年當選總統，所以再次回到福德祠參拜，也有「還願」的成分在。<br />\n<br />\n文章提到，對於蔡英文這種「不問蒼生問鬼神」的行為，有網友質問「壞事做多了，神明會原諒你嗎？」上台2年多以來，她都做了哪些「壞事」；從最初不承認「九二共識」到喊出「用愛發電」、「年金改革」，再到「新課改」中「去中國化」，以及讓「各國聯手制約大陸」等，都早已引起兩岸民眾極大不滿。<br />\n<br />\n連親綠的「台灣民意基金會」民調都顯示，蔡英文聲望深陷低迷，支持率跌至33%，不支持率飆至52%。讓人不禁想問，這2年多來，蔡英文當局究竟在折騰啥？經濟糟糕、生活質量下降、民眾抗議。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，今天廣大台灣同胞對大陸發展進步的關注，對「惠台31條」的歡迎，同他們對民進黨當局兩岸政策憂慮之深、對民進黨執政失望之大、對台灣經濟民生不滿意度之高，形成鮮明對比，原因是什麼？不言而喻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180704/1205256.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180704%2F1205256.htm&d=rsDJBa8lbVk3udcJb1DQEwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=937e57e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180704/1205256.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fbkhUL8NuPHEiMLxlibReA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDgwO2g9Mjcw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/Appappapps.com/5710792765a788a6fba4340c76be7d58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfbkhUL8NuPHEiMLxlibReA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDgwO2g9Mjcw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2FAppappapps.com%2F5710792765a788a6fba4340c76be7d58&h=2febe886&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eac5be102089520c19fc106a890087fd48263bc","tid":729833,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/29173354/Presentation1-1-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F29173354%2FPresentation1-1-4.jpg&h=f6feddcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ce5f01257eb86a4194e29129a049349a073df38","tid":729833,"uid":37820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"中國人當毛魔係神咁拜啦"},{"pid":"e9bc6934f771b9d1ecc26265a74ecc567e5a549a","tid":729833,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2ce5f01257eb86a4194e29129a049349a073df38","tid":729833,"uid":37820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"中國人當毛魔係神咁拜啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T01:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://caiguanhao.files.wordpress.com/2011/04/dsc05217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcaiguanhao.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F04%2Fdsc05217.jpg&h=f043b5b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0044f46c601aeab5255aa9c7782c6b094f2f6d72","tid":729833,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"又玩無神論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40aaca08b165ee0a15f367a407bd82237f1a8b0","tid":729833,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"淫民日報又打曬飛機"},{"pid":"f235f2028b654b4975087d503d9bd602599b4f2a","tid":729833,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"中国人口講不問鬼神，但不停神化吹噓領導層"},{"pid":"2372967627348aa849c31d96d30acd09b347f61e","tid":729833,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"所以我認為梵帝岡同蔡英文蛇鼠一窩，中央應該懲罰梵帝岡唔好同佢見交"},{"pid":"4c98f143ee8d55d4f15bdf30e7f816dd91dac9f1","tid":729833,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:28:04.000Z","msg"